net.entersol.gdbc
Class Gdbc

java.lang.Object
  net.entersol.gdbc.Gdbc
All Implemented Interfaces:
IOResponce
public class Gdbc
extends Object
implements IOResponce

This class is directly responsible of sending queries to the server via an IOGate and Receiving results from server as json object request object has this format 

 {
        db: String //database name,
        index: integer // index of transaction,
        total: integer // total number of statements,
        queries:[
                                query1: { 
                                                method : String // direct or indirect,
                                                sql : String // sql statment or index of the saved query at server
                                                },
                                query2: { 
                                                method : String // direct or indirect,
                                                sql : String // sql statment or index of the saved query at server
                                                },
                                query#: { 
                                                method : String // direct or indirect,
                                                sql : String // sql statment or index of the saved query at server
                                                }
                        ]
 }

Received object has this format

 
 {
        db: String //database name,
        index: integer // index of transaction,
        total: integer // total number of statements,
        queries:[
                                query1: { 
                                                method : String // direct or indirect,
                                                sql : {
                                                                results : [1st Row, 2nd Row],
                                                        lastInsertId : an integer or null,
                                                        rowCount: an integer
                                                           }
                                                },
                                query2: { 
                                                method : String // direct or indirect,
                                                sql : {
                                                                results : [1st Row, 2nd Row],
                                                        lastInsertId : an integer or null,
                                                        rowCount: an integer
                                                           }
                                                },
                                query#: { 
                                                method : String // direct or indirect,
                                                sql : {
                                                                results : [1st Row, 2nd Row],
                                                        lastInsertId : an integer or null,
                                                        rowCount: an integer
                                                           }
                                                }
                        ]
 }
